            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d22277-Hd1e108">Rubrica 13</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d22277-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De culpa et excusatione</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d22277-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="75"/>
      ¶ De culpa et excusatione. Rubrica. 13 
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d22277-d1e119">
               <lb ed="#V" n="76"/>
      <ref>¶ TUllius rethori. artis veter
      <lb ed="#V" n="77" break="no"/>ris li. i. c. 12.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d22277-Qd1e125">His
        <lb ed="#V" n="78"/>qui imprudentes leserunt ignosci con
        <lb ed="#V" n="79" break="no"/>uenit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d22277-d1e133"> <ref>/ Li. 2. c. 5.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d22277-Qd1e135">Nihil est indi
        <lb ed="#V" n="80" break="no"/>gnius quam eum qui culpa caret supplicio non
        <lb ed="#V" n="81"/>carere.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d22277-d1e144"> <ref>/ Idem retho. artis noue li. 2 ca. 7.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="82"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d22277-Qd1e146">Uoluntario facinori nulla est excusatio: im
        <lb ed="#V" n="83" break="no"/>prudentie et iniusta depraecatio parata est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d22277-d1e154"> <ref>/ Idem
        <lb ed="#V" n="84"/>inuectiua in salustium</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d22277-Qd1e156">Non procacitate lin
        <lb ed="#V" n="85" break="no"/>gue sordes eluuntur.</quote>
        <lb ed="#V" n="86"/><ref>¶ Seneca tragediarum in epido. ca. 14. et fi.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="87"/> <quote>Nemo fit fato nocens.</quote> <ref>In hercule etheo. c.
        <lb ed="#V" n="88"/>8.</ref> <quote>Error a culpa vacat.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d22277-d1e170"> <ref>/ Idem epistolarum ad
        <lb ed="#V" n="89"/>lucillum li. 19. e. 10.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d22277-Qd1e172">Uitia nostra quia ama
        <lb ed="#V" n="90" break="no"/>mus defendimus: et malumus excusare illa <!--85.xml-->
        <pb ed="#V" n="29-v"/>
                  <cb ed="#V" n="a"/>
                  <lb ed="#V" n="1"/>quam excutere.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d22277-d1e189"> <ref>/ Idem declam. li. 7. in proemio</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="2"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d22277-Qd1e191">Hoc equale omnium est vt vitia sua excusa
        <lb ed="#V" n="3" break="no"/>re malint quam effugare.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d22277-d1e199"> <ref>/ Idem de namlibus
        <lb ed="#V" n="4"/>quodnibus li. 4.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d22277-Qd1e201">Nihil tam manifeste vtilitat
        <lb ed="#V" n="5"/>est quod non incontrarium transeat culpa.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d22277-d1e209">
               <lb ed="#V" n="6"/>
                <ref>¶ Ualerius max. li. 9. c. 9.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d22277-Qd1e213">Error non sua spon
        <lb ed="#V" n="7" break="no"/>te: sed vanis incitatus imaginibus culpe se
        <lb ed="#V" n="8"/>implicat.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d22277-d1e222">
               <lb ed="#V" n="9"/>
               <ref>¶ Lex diges. ti. ad leg. iul. maie. l. famosi. §. i.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="10"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d22277-Qd1e226">Lubricum lingue facile ad penam trahendum non
        <lb ed="#V" n="11"/>est.</quote> <ref>/ Ti. de reg. iu. li. l. infrascriptur.</ref> <quote>Culpa est im
        <lb ed="#V" n="12" break="no"/>miscere rei ad se non pertinenti. Imperi
        <lb ed="#V" n="13" break="no"/>tia culpe annumeratur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d22277-d1e238">
               <lb ed="#V" n="14"/>
                <ref>¶ Cecilius firmianus de beata vita libro. 6.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="15"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d22277-Qd1e242">Natura hominum procliuis in vitia videri
        <lb ed="#V" n="16"/>vult: non modo cum venia: sed etiam cum ratione peccatur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d22277-d1e250">
               <lb ed="#V" n="17"/>
               <ref>¶ Prosper sub vlt. c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d22277-Qd1e254">Insontem vitam: pacis
        <lb ed="#V" n="18"/>amator agit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d22277-d1e260">
               <lb ed="#V" n="19"/>
                <ref>¶ Cassiodorus epistolarum li. 4. e. 7.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d22277-Qd1e264">Iniquum
        <lb ed="#V" n="20"/>est vt hominis vitio deputetur quod eius voluntate
        <lb ed="#V" n="21"/>non regitur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d22277-d1e272"> <ref>/ Li. 5. e. 36.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d22277-Qd1e274">Non est ignauie
        <lb ed="#V" n="22"/>culpa quam excusat miseranda calamitas.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d22277-d1e280"> <ref>/ Li.
        <lb ed="#V" n="23"/>9. e. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d22277-Qd1e282">Uix audet quisquam in illos exercere: in
        <lb ed="#V" n="24"/>quibus culpas non potest inuenire.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d22277-d1e291">
               <lb ed="#V" n="25"/>
                <ref>¶ Andreas capellanus ad gualterium de amo
        <lb ed="#V" n="26" break="no"/>re li. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d22277-Qd1e295">Importuna necessitas nulla potest iu
        <lb ed="#V" n="27" break="no"/>ris regula coartari.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d22277-d1e303">
               <lb ed="#V" n="28"/>
               <ref>¶ Montenarius in luna cleri. c. 82.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d22277-Qd1e307">Auget
        <lb ed="#V" n="29"/>non minuit mala consuetudo reatum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d22277-d1e313">
               <lb ed="#V" n="30"/>
                <ref>¶ Gualterius de castellione li. 3.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d22277-Qd1e317">Uis illata
        <lb ed="#V" n="31"/>leuat minuitque coactio culpam.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d22277-d1e323">
               <lb ed="#V" n="32"/>
               <ref>¶ Prouerb. metrice extra or. lib. vag.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d22277-Qd1e327">Ultra
        <lb ed="#V" n="33"/>posse suum nullum lex equa coegit.</quote>
            </p>
         </div>
